<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>しまいの窓口 | LINE相談</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      background: #f5f3f0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 420px;
      width: 90%;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 40px 28px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #2d2d2d;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .message {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #444;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .line-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #06C755;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 16px 40px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      transition: background 0.2s;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .line-btn:hover { background: #05b34c; }
    .note {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #aaa;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo">しまいの窓口</div>
    <div class="subtitle">ご遺族の手続きサポート</div>
    <p class="message">
      LINEで無料相談ができます。<br>
      下のボタンを押して友だち追加してください。
    </p>
    <a class="line-btn" href="https://line.me/R/oaMessage/%40557zpmsr/?ota_seikatsu_hogo">LINEで相談する</a>
    <p class="note">※ボタンを押すとLINEアプリが開きます</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
